              "displayName": "Remus Rusanu",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Europe/Bucharest"
            },
            "body": "This patch adds ValidateLocalPath function, checks all file operations for valid paths, and adds a yarn.nodemanager.windows-secure-container-executor.local-dirs key in wsce-site.xml. The SecureContainer.apt.vm is updated to describe the new config key.",
